OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FQuite cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fsome rain. Variable amounts of cloud
OL,7,Fand sunny spells in the afternoon
OL,8,Falong with scattered slow moving
OL,9,Fshowers, occasionally heavy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FScattered heavy showers will
OL,12,Fgradually die out this evening,
OL,13,Fleaving the rest of the night largely
OL,14,Fdry with a few clear spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping. Light winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA mainly dry, bright
OL,18,Fmorning. Turning overcast through the
OL,19,Fafternoon as a band of occasionally
OL,20,Fheavy rain spreads in from the west
OL,21,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
