OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBright and breezy on Thursday with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and a few
OL,8,Fscattered showers. Risk of patchy rain
OL,9,Fon Friday and Saturday.
